---
/**
 * HeroCard.astro
 * ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 * ORGANISM — Hero / Header section card.
 * Based on BaseCard — same visual spec, specific to the hero section.
 *
 * Visual spec (Figma):
 *   Size    → 913 × 274px (max-w / min-h)
 *   Fill    → bg-white (#FDFDF9, --color-white) — no grid texture shown
 *             base-card-grid applies the matching inner grid overlay
 *   Stroke  → ring-[5px] ring-grey  (5px outside, #E6E7F2)
 *   Radius  → rounded-r-[2rem] md:rounded-r-[2.5rem] rounded-l-none
 *             Left edge flush with canvas left boundary.
 *   Shadow  → base-card-shadow (inner + drop)
 *   Blur    → base-card-blur (0.5px)
 *   Grid    → base-card-grid (matching inner skewed grid)
 *
 * Arbitrary value justifications:
 *   [913px]  Figma frame width
 *   [274px]  Figma frame height
 *   [2rem]/[2.5rem]  Consistent with canvas card radius language
 *   [5px]    User-specified stroke width
 * ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 */
---

<article
  class="bg-white ring-[5px] ring-grey rounded-r-[2rem] md:rounded-r-[2.5rem] rounded-l-none max-w-[913px] w-full md:w-[56%] min-h-[274px] base-card-shadow base-card-blur base-card-grid relative"
  aria-label="Hero section card"
>
  <!-- Slot content — visually above the grid ::before layer (z-10) -->
  <div class="relative z-10 h-full p-6">
    <slot />
  </div>
</article>
